        "description": "Did you ever want to feel like a powerful mage as you explore dungeons, fighting scary monsters and discovering long lost treasure?\n\nMythic Mage is a dungeon crawler with procedurally generated levels. Fight monsters using melee or ranged attacks! Face giant bosses! Upgrade your stats between floors! But beware: if you die, you start again from the beginning!\n\nUnlock permanent upgrades and new enemies the further you get in the dungeon. How far can you get before you perish?\n\nFeatures:\n★ Infinite procedurally generated dungeons!\n★ Terrifying monsters to battle!\n★ Environmental hazards!\n★ Shop to upgrade abilities during a run!\n★ Permanent upgrades and unlocks that stay between runs!",
